column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, ga.oiii_#_flux, ga.oiii_#_flux_err,         (sph.dered_g-sph.dered_r) as col_g_r,         sph.dered_g-#*log1#(#E+#*sph.z)+# as M_g  FROM  GalSpecLine as ga, specobj as s, Galaxy as g, SpecPhoto as sph  WHERE ga.oiii_#_flux >#*ga.oiii_#_flux_err   AND ga.oiii_#_flux <#*ga.oiii_#_flux_err   AND s.class = &&&   AND s.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND s.specobjid = g.specobjid    AND sph.specobjid = g.specobjid   AND sph.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND ga.oiii_#_flux_err > #   AND g.specobjid > #   AND sph.z > #  into MyDB.dataml_t
